# Cloudflare Pages SPA Fallback Rules
# Explicit asset rules BEFORE fallback to prevent infinite loop

# Static assets - serve as-is
/assets/*  /assets/:splat  200
/favicon*  /favicon:splat  200
/logo*     /logo:splat     200
/icons/*   /icons/:splat   200
/images/*  /images/:splat  200

# Static files
/robots.txt    /robots.txt    200
/sitemap.xml   /sitemap.xml   200
/manifest.webmanifest  /manifest.webmanifest  200

# SPA fallback - MUST be last
/*  /index.html  200
